Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Require npm

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 40
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"
Set WindowBar Rings

Sleep 1s

Type "opencli run '/plan add a test function for the context compactor'"
Enter

Sleep 8s

Type "y"
Enter

Sleep 5s

Type "/exit"
Enter

Sleep 1s
